channel.title: Webs Webclient help
channel.description: Hey, so I made my web-client and it works perfectly fine but whenever I load it on webs.com it cuts off a bit at the end, it wouldn't be a problem usually except that it's Galkon's Refractored Client that has a 400 something game frame. So stuff like the mage book and log out button gets cut. If anyone can help me or tell me another website that you can upload client.jar and html to, that would be epic thanks.
